ED_Title: Comprehensive review of the whole  question of peacekeeping operations in all their aspects
ED_DecisionText:
At its 47th plenary meeting, on 4 December 2024, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Special
Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee).  (Footnote: A/79/424.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/79/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
